{"id":27498677758,"name":"Test","node_id":"WFR_kwLOA_1uaM8AAAAGZwyF_g","head_branch":"ci/sonar-fork-pr-analysis","head_sha":"a68198590858a2bbce7e309109730041e425528c","path":".github/workflows/run-tests.yml","run_number":54172,"run_attempt":1,"event":"pull_request","display_title":"ci: run SonarCloud PR analysis for fork pull requests","status":"completed","conclusion":"cancelled","workflow_id":10954,"check_suite_id":73991422954,"check_suite_node_id":"CS_kwDOA_1uaM8AAAAROjuD6g","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758","created_at":"2026-06-14T12:21:22Z","updated_at":"2026-06-14T12:25:55Z","run_started_at":"2026-06-14T12:21:22Z","jobs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758/jobs","logs_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758/logs","check_suite_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/check-suites/73991422954","artifacts_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758/artifacts","cancel_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758/cancel","rerun_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/runs/27498677758/rerun","head_commit":{"message":"ci: run SonarCloud PR analysis for fork pull requests\n\nPRs opened from forks fail the SonarCloud check: GitHub does not expose\nrepository secrets (DHIS2_BOT_SONARCLOUD_TOKEN) to pull_request runs\ntriggered by a fork, so the token guard in analyse-pr.yml hard-fails.\n\nSplit the PR path into the two-workflow pattern SonarSource recommends\nfor forks:\n\n- analyse-pr.yml (pull_request, no secrets): builds the PR and uploads\n  the built workspace + PR metadata + sibling SNAPSHOT module artifacts\n  as an artifact. The long-living-branch (push/dispatch) analysis still\n  runs inline, where secrets are available.\n- analyse-pr-sonar.yml (workflow_run): runs in the base-repo context\n  with the token, downloads the artifact and runs `mvn sonar:sonar`,\n  decorating the originating PR.\n\nThe untrusted PR build runs without the token. workflow_run always uses\nthe default-branch workflow definition, so a fork cannot alter the\nanalysis steps.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"stian-sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"a68198590858a2bbce7e309109730041e425528c","tree_id":"32459d4b3fbf08e70ec796b67b2760dfaf8ed64b","timestamp":"2026-06-14T10:24:34Z","committer":{"name":"stian-sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhis2/dhis2-core","description":"DHIS 2 Core. Written in Java. Contains the service layer and Web API.","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2/dhis2-core","fork":false,"private":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core","archive_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core